column5: If you play the same numbers again this week ...you might win at least half that amount again...lol...Congrates....get a tetanus shot though...rusty horse shoes can cause some serious problems in that location
Very nice Lew, congrats!
Just to add to the fun and if anyone really cares, my wife won another $170 last night. I'm leaving on Saturday for a 2 week musky trip to the West Arm  and if this continues it'll be a freebee
Unreal. Are you a Statistician? Quick-pic?
Same numbers all the time & alot of luck
that's it Lew, show us the tickets!
That's how much Lotto 649 gave me last night.  Retirement just keeps getting better every day
congratulation Lew nothing like getting someone else to pay for your next fishing trip or two.   Art
Nice!
Congrats Lew, about time I herd someone that I know win Couldn't happen to a better guy.
We won $2600 a few years back too, must be a horseshoe hidden around here somewhere
Lew, I have a few fishing rods that need a magic touch
Wow, lucky you!!  That's fantastic Lew!
Lew Lew Lew....I'm sure you can find another $1807 that you forgot you had in a socks drawer somewhere.   Congrats!
You've got a great memory Roy hahaha
Is it wrong that my brain automatically translated your winnings in dollars into 5 x St. Croix LT rods? Lol... congrats Lew!  Pete
I don't think it's wrong Pete, but my wife might, and you know what they say about wives & purse strings
Did you lose 10 bucks somewhere Lew...I read it was $1817 on facebook...LOL
That will come in handy i'm sure , congrats !
hate to be the devils advocate here but did you get back what you spent over the last year ?  Some people spend many $$$$ on the big lottos.
Could be I read it wrong Norm, the old eyes ain't what they used to be  And no darsky, we're well ahead of the game.
Congrats!
Well done Lew!  10 to 12 of us have been kicking in $5 each every week for at least 4 or 5 years.Nothing ever over $80 bucks.I guess we are a bunch of hard luck cases

I think good luck runs in my family.  18 months ago my daughter won an all expense paid vacation for 2 to Freeport, Bahamas, and they no longer got home from there and she won another all in trip for 2 to Los Angeles.
Congrats Lew,we play same numbers on 649 every draw for years.I'm sure a small windfall is in the cards sometime soon.
That's awesome for you Lew!!! Congrats!  It rocks to win money, I got a lucky feeling last bought a ticket it won me 120 ...cant imagine break'n 1000 :-)
We still can't lol.  .someday,maybe.
That's a nice chunk of change, enjoy it with the Mrs!
Hey Lew, CONGRATS!  Nice pay day for ya.  Whatchya spending it on?
Sweet Lew!
awesome lew congrats
